{"tid":1438284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發］北角警署白網冧咗","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:33:45.000Z","uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a06b63b8eefeef405c1bf6f7f186c5f18484575","tid":1438284,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:28:12.000Z","msg":"對唔住引咗你入黎睇。<br />\n<br />\n即係咁，啲poopoo咁無聊咒自己就黎歸天蓋白網呢件事認真係八月第一膠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個白網其實好易黏實豆漿，牛奶，雞蛋，而啲高蛋白質嘅東西，又易發臭又引來大量蟲和老鼠、蟻、蟑螂等等～<br />\n<br />\n如果巴打絲打扔呢啲嘢入去，應該會有好好嘅效果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a35b7b9fd18e706c27c70e8abe5d5b2fe722f2","tid":1438284,"uid":300956,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老未五毛"},{"pid":"da7a7bd3c1e037b67f68ec24c82d68c03e9a5840","tid":1438284,"uid":290323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:33:45.000Z","msg":"標題狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}